data.description: This stunning home has been upgraded and move in ready. Step inside to see the spacious living room, that opens to a formal dining room and living room.  The upgraded kitchen  features newer flooring, a center island,  upgraded light features, granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances,  and a sunny breakfast nook next to the patio doors.  The open concept flows to a generous-sized family room, featuring  recessed lighting and a vaulted ceiling and a half bath on the first floor.  The master suite includes a walk in closet and full bath.  Four spacious bedrooms and two full baths compolete the second floor.  The garage offers plent of storage space. Outside of the sliding glass doors is an expansive deck that overlooks the huge back yard. The home sits on a corner lot next to a wooded lot.  Enjoy a secluded feeling while still getting the neighnorhood feel.  Security cameras and security system , Ac unit installed in 2020.  Location could not be better with easy access to all major highways for your commute. This community is conviently located between Philadelphia and the Jersey Shore.  Professional photos and virtual tour coming in the next couple of days.
